 <metadata>
  <name>RTR - RNR, Bury, Tesco, Ringley, Stand</name>
  <desc>Head up RNR at the top turn right on to Bury New Road.  Follow the road toward Prestwich until you get to Tesco.  Turn around and head back going left at McDonalds up Higher Lane, then left on to Ringley Road and then right on to Stand Lane.  From here follow the road back to the market.</desc>
  <author>
   <name>Paul Cox</name>
   <link href="https://www.strava.com/athletes/90628842"/>
  </author>
